I spent some time studying the geometry of the dodecahedron, and thinking about how the LED strip snakes around it. Each edge will contain 17 LEDS at 144LED/M, so total LEDs will be 510. I analyzed a useful wiring diagram that I found online so I could understand how the data signal flows through the entire structure.

